data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom home that has forest service right behind it. Fully fenced large yard.Seller has a 3% assumable VA loan. Large master bedroom with double vanities in the master bath and walk-in closet. Rapid City school bus picks up right on the corner of Nemo road and Chipmunk. Kitchen has a huge pantry. Large deck across the front of the house that makes it perfect for relaxing evenings. Home also comes with a water softener and reverse osmosis. Call today to set up your personal showing.
